{"tid":344971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國最高專員公署 突然舉傘","createTime":"2017-08-02T16:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T01:05:41.000Z","uid":92301,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c410de8fb597a5fd61cba1926919e4eaca5280","tid":344971,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"英國最高專員公署 嘅facebook，突然貼出一張相，喺南巴斯嘅一個舉傘裝置設計，更要引用陳百強脈搏奔流呢首歌。如果無任何政治解讀，大家或者以為係純粹嘅一個旅遊推廣post。如果係旅遊推廣post， 英國最高專員公署 仲唔勁寫UK is Great之類嘅嘢咩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英國最高專員公署 意有所指</span><br />\n<br />\n彭定康獲委任為香港總督前，佢不單係保守黨主席，仲要係Bath嘅MP嚟，佢係因為Sainsbury&rsquo;s百貨公司老闆指明要玩殘彭定康，至係當年保守黨於彭定康指揮下贏開巷嘅情況下，竟然彭定康自己保唔住議席。而大家都知，喺2014年海富催淚彈大戰後，雨傘喺香港有乜意思，所以至叫做遮打革命，或者雨傘革命。再加上歌詞，成件事你話無政治含意，英國佬出post一向好小心，特別FCO (Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office) 有咁多親華派，但依家好明顯，英國係另有算盤，我諗遲啲嘅post，就更清楚。英國唔同德國，德國柏林抽香港水已經係國策，但一向以嚟，英國都好小心處理對香港政府嘅評論。<br />\n<br />\n當然，英國呢個post嘅背景，其實唔難理解，大家都知道，BREXIT without freedom of movement將會係大災難，但英格蘭班鄉下佬攞到公投結果也文也武，文翠珊依家投其所好，都只會令佢提早玩完，特別對歐洲國家嚟講，freedom of movement係寸步不讓，呢個問題幾乎係無得傾，話雖英國佬自己無認真用晒2004/38/EC賦予嘅immigration control權力，至係BREXIT嘅罪魁禍首嚟。既然依家好難搵到嘢可以㩒停BREXIT呢個瘋狂行為，咁依家唯有可能出高調重新干預香港，如果有香港爭奪戰，就有機會將BREXIT㩒停。由伊莉沙白二世號航空母艦，到依家呢個post，都睇到好一致嘅國策，如果八月至十月，BREXIT仍然係傾出膠嘅話，加上特朗普打算要習近平找數，我個人相信，香港爭奪戰只不過係遲早問題，屆時英國要出手嘅話，一定要做好Heart and Mind嘅準備。呢個係十分典型英式玩法。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以繼續留意事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/15515/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2-%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E8%88%89%E5%82%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F15515%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2584%25B6%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2582%2598&d=PbC1aPS5YihWYmaKu%2BFY7HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1e4b8654\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/15515/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2-%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E8%88%89%E5%82%98</a>"},{"pid":"3f819dcbef6f3d661897d528f2c31ca84b9f8ed4","tid":344971,"uid":92301,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20525212_1497958440247579_9075416971758141176_n.jpg?oh=1a417ca2fe243928dc96f155dde1b30f&amp;oe=59F4F910\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20525212_1497958440247579_9075416971758141176_n.jpg%3Foh%3D1a417ca2fe243928dc96f155dde1b30f%26oe%3D59F4F910&h=6cf12f41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24fa727501a351bed0145357cac0ce7d7df3247","tid":344971,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"UK in Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UKandHongKong/photos/a.153141311395972.28962.153101271399976/1497958440247579/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUKandHongKong%2Fphotos%2Fa.153141311395972.28962.153101271399976%2F1497958440247579%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=PbC1aPS5YihWYmaKu%2BFY7HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d1d05bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UKandHongKong/photos/a.153141311395972.28962.153101271399976/1497958440247579/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"bc8c926fed39a93b016dc8b806a475b5549edd7e","tid":344971,"uid":52349,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"就咁睇標題都知邊個係作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81b1010e1eef66065d37b21b962f9906f4ca158","tid":344971,"uid":25582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:13:29.000Z","msg":"我住果頭都有樓上呢d雨傘"},{"pid":"0b7323a6e3f2205e1bb1b96e884b1847ce65da1c","tid":344971,"uid":55120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"FF得太多"},{"pid":"64dae3e3924b7c098162ccadecdffaf168dc5d02","tid":344971,"uid":54024,"like":6,"